To install:

1. Go into the directory you wish
2. git init
3. git pull git://github.com/tareko/Kitab-Al-Shifa.git
4. mkdir app/webroot/pdf
5. Either
	a. chown www-data.www-data app/webroot/pdf   # or
	b. chmod 777 app/webroot/pdf

6. As above, can either use chown or chmod technique to make the 
following directories, which have to be writable by your webserver:
	a. mkdir app/tmp
	b. mkdir app/tmp/cache
	c. mkdir app/tmp/cache/persistent
	d. mkdir app/tmp/cache/models
	e. mkdir app/tmp/logs
	f. mkdir app/tmp/sessions
	g. mkdir app/tmp/tests

7. Config directory
	a. cp app/Config/core.php.default app/Config/core.php
	b. cp app/Config/database.php.default app/Config/database.php.default
	c. cp app/Config/email.php.default app/Config/email.php

8. Add the kitab.sql scheme and Joomla scheme if needed
